---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Services | Jeremy Dubs — Web Design, Content Production & Digital Strategy" description="Custom web design, original content production, and AI-powered digital strategy for businesses, brands, and creators.">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="label">Services</span>
      <h1>Design. Content. <em>Strategy.</em></h1>
      <p>Everything your business needs to show up better online — from the website itself, to the content on it, to the strategy behind it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WEB DESIGN -->
  <section id="web-design">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="label">01 — Primary</span>
        <h2 style="margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;">Web Design & <em>Development</em></h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Custom websites built on modern frameworks — fast, clean, and designed to convert.</p>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);">I design and build websites from scratch using Astro, static HTML, and Webflow — depending on what fits. Every site is custom-designed, performance-optimized, and built with SEO fundamentals baked in. No templates, no page builders, no bloated WordPress installs.</p>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);">I also redesign and rebuild existing sites that have fallen behind — fixing what's broken, rewriting copy, restructuring content, and modernizing the experience.</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; padding: 1.25rem; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-sm);">
          <strong style="font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: var(--accent);">What's Included</strong>
          <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0.5rem 0 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">Custom design · Responsive development · SEO & performance · Copy guidance · Content integration · Hosting setup · Post-launch support</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; padding: 1.25rem; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-sm);">
          <strong style="font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: var(--accent);">Best For</strong>
          <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0.5rem 0 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">Businesses launching a new site, companies with outdated sites that need a full rebuild, brands that want something custom and fast without agency overhead.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;"><a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Start a Web Project</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTENT PRODUCTION -->
  <section id="content" style="background: var(--bg-elevated);">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="label">02 — Integrated</span>
        <h2 style="margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;">Content <em>Production</em></h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Original photo, video, and drone content — produced for your website and marketing.</p>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);">A website is only as good as what's on it. I produce professional video, photography, and aerial drone content — formatted for your site, social media, and paid ads. This isn't a separate service bolted on. It's integrated into the same engagement, so everything is consistent and built with purpose.</p>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);">I've spent over a decade in video production — commercials, brand films, real estate tours, event coverage, and social content. I edit in Premiere Pro and DaVinci Resolve, and I'm FAA Part 107 licensed for drone work.</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; padding: 1.25rem; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-sm);">
          <strong style="font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: var(--accent);">What I Produce</strong>
          <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0.5rem 0 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">Brand video · Social reels & ads · Product/service photography · Aerial drone coverage · Event coverage · Remote editing · Multi-format delivery</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;"><a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book a Shoot</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AI & STRATEGY -->
  <section id="strategy">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="label">03 — Strategic</span>
        <h2 style="margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;">AI & Digital <em>Strategy</em></h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Modernize how you work and how you show up online.</p>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);">AI is changing how businesses create content, build websites, and operate online. I help companies understand what's actually useful — and implement it. Not hype, not theory. Practical AI integration into real workflows: content creation, development acceleration, automation, and digital presence strategy.</p>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);">This can be a standalone engagement or built into a web design project. Either way, the goal is the same — help you move faster and show up smarter.</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; padding: 1.25rem; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-sm);">
          <strong style="font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: var(--accent);">What This Looks Like</strong>
          <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0.5rem 0 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">AI workflow audit · Content automation setup · Digital presence review · Tool recommendations · Website strategy · Growth roadmap</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;"><a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Let's Talk Strategy</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-block" style="background: var(--bg-elevated);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="reveal">Not sure what you <em>need?</em></h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 2rem;" class="reveal">Tell me what you're working on and I'll recommend the right approach. No pitch — just an honest assessment.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary reveal">Start a Conversation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
